This is a (multiple allowed):

* [x] bug
* [ ] enhancement
* [ ] feature-discussion (RFC)

* CakePHP Version: 4.0.1 Stable
* Platform and Target: (xampp 7.4.1 Windows 10), PHP 7.4.1, Apache 2.4.41, MariaDB 10.4.11

### What you did
I am trying to use the pagination helper with an modified url. 

### What happened
All buttons work correctly except the first and last buttons. This is my code:
```php
<?= $this->Paginator->first('<< ' . __('Primera'),['model'=>$model,'escape' => false,'url'=>$url]) ?>
<?= $this->Paginator->prev('< ' . __('Anterior'),['model'=>$model,'escape' => false,'url'=>$url]) ?>
<?= $this->Paginator->numbers(['model'=>$model, 'escape' => false,'url'=>$url, ] ) ?>
<?= $this->Paginator->next(__('Siguiente') . ' >',['model'=>$model,'escape' => false,'url'=>$url]) ?>
<?= $this->Paginator->last(__('Ãšltima') . ' >>',['model'=>$model,'escape' => false,'url'=>$url]) ?>
```


### What you expected to happen
The first and the last buttons do not generated the modified url, the generate the not modified one.

I solved it by modifying the file vendor/cakephp/cakephp/src/View/Helper/PaginationHelper.php. The original code was:
lines 1065-1078:
```php
if (is_int($first) && $params['page'] >= $first) {
	for ($i = 1; $i <= $first; $i++) {
		$out .= $this->templater()->format('number', [
			'url' => $this->generateUrl(['page' => $i], $options['model'], $options['url']),
			'text' => $this->Number->format($i),
		]);
	}
} elseif ($params['page'] > 1 && is_string($first)) {
	$first = $options['escape'] ? h($first) : $first;
	$out .= $this->templater()->format('first', [
		'url' => $this->generateUrl(['page' => 1], $options['model']),
		'text' => $first,
	]);
}
```
lines 1125-1138:
```php
if (is_int($last) && $params['page'] <= $lower) {
	for ($i = $lower; $i <= $params['pageCount']; $i++) {
		$out .= $this->templater()->format('number', [
			'url' => $this->generateUrl(['page' => $i], $options['model'], $options['url']),
			'text' => $this->Number->format($i),
		]);
	}
} elseif ($params['page'] < $params['pageCount'] && is_string($last)) {
	$last = $options['escape'] ? h($last) : $last;
	$out .= $this->templater()->format('last', [
		'url' => $this->generateUrl(['page' => $params['pageCount']], $options['url']),
		'text' => $last,
	]);
}
```

and the edited code to solve the problem
lines 1065-1078:
```php
if (is_int($first) && $params['page'] >= $first) {
	for ($i = 1; $i <= $first; $i++) {
		$out .= $this->templater()->format('number', [
